org.spongepowered.api.potion

Interface PotionEffect

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DataSerializable, ImmutableDataHolder<PotionEffect>, ImmutableValueStore<PotionEffect,ImmutableDataManipulator<?,?>>, ValueContainer<PotionEffect>

    public interface PotionEffect
extends DataSerializable, ImmutableDataHolder<PotionEffect>
    Represents an effect of a PotionEffectType for a specified getDuration(), getAmplifier(), and getShowParticles(). The PotionEffect itself is immutable once created and can be offered to Entity instances through the PotionEffectData.
